Korgel Blackblade leads a team of twenty war [[troll]]s trained by [[Sora Maenya]] herself, a unit which forms the true core of the [[Flayer Guard]] of [[Graywall]]. Korgel is a war troll of terrifying skill and power, who wields a magic greatsword forged by [[Szalas Jal]].